ripctl(8)	1/2


Client connecting to ripd via unix domain socket
query runtime information
(de)couple kernel routing table
show interfaces/neighbors states

Useful to inspect or debug what is going on in your network

Useful to get any kind of information about neighbors, interfaces state and many other things 

